items that autocurse are:\n\n* [[Loadstone]]s (appearance: 회색 돌)\n* [[Helm of opposite alignment|Helms of opposite alignment]] ([[randomized appearance]])\n* [[Dunce cap]]s (appearance: [[conical hat|원뿔 모자]])\n\nThe helm and the dunce cap will become cursed when [[wear|worn]] by a player, while the loadstone only becomes cursed when dropped - that is, picking up an uncursed loadstone is perfectly safe. However, since all loadstones are generated cursed (except possibly those in containers), they are still best left alone. 만약 당신이 [[wizard]], you can safely ignore all conical hats, since the only other hat that shares that appearance is the [[cornuthaum]], which is only beneficial to [[wizard]]s or to give [[large]]-sized [[pet]]s [[magic cancellation]].\n\n==더 보기==\n\n* [[scroll of scare monster]], which also changes [[beatitude]] when dropped by players\n[[Category:Item attributes]]\n{{nethack-343}}\n[[Category:한국어]]"}